SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'SALES' THEN sl.QTY ELSE 0 END) AS QTY, SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'WASCANCEL' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'SALES' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) AS VOID_AMT FROM BIA_RTL.DWB_RTL_SL_RETRN_LINE_ITEM sl, BIA_RTL.DWR_TCHPNT tch, BIA_RTL.DWR_USERS users, BIA_RTL.DWR_ORG_BSNS_UNIT_X_ATTR str WHERE sl.TCHPNT_KEY = tch.TCHPNT_KEY AND tch.POS_TYP NOT IN ('SCO') AND sl.RTL_TYP_CD IN('WASCANCEL', 'SALES') AND sl.BSNS_UNIT_KEY = str.ORG_BSNS_UNIT_KEY AND sl.OPERATOR_USER_KEY = users.USERS_KEY AND sl.DAY_KEY BETWEEN '20180305' AND '20180311' GROUP BY sl.DAY_KEY, str.BSNS_UNIT_CD, tch.POS_TYP, users.USER_NBR, sl.SKU_ITEM_KEY, sl.TRX_NBR HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_C D = 'WASCANCEL' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'SALES' THEN sl.QTY ELSE 0 END) AS QTY, SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'WASCANCEL' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'SALES' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) AS VOID_AMT FROM BIA_RTL.DWB_RTL_SL_RETRN_LINE_ITEM sl, BIA_RTL.DWR_TCHPNT tch, BIA_RTL.DWR_USERS users, BIA_RTL.DWR_ORG_BSNS_UNIT_X_ATTR str WHERE sl.TCHPNT_KEY = tch.TCHPNT_KEY AND tch.POS_TYP NOT IN ('SCO') AND sl.RTL_TYP_CD IN('WASCANCEL', 'SALES') AND sl.BSNS_UNIT_KEY = str.ORG_BSNS_UNIT_KEY AND sl.OPERATOR_USER_KEY = users.USERS_KEY AND sl.DAY_KEY BETWEEN '20180226' AND '20180304' GROUP BY sl.DAY_KEY, str.BSNS_UNIT_CD, tch.POS_TYP, users.USER_NBR, sl.SKU_ITEM_KEY, sl.TRX_NBR HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_C D = 'WASCANCEL' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN sl.RTL_TYP_CD = 'SALES' THEN sl.ACTUAL_AMT ELSE 0 END) BETWEEN 2 AND 50 ), pts AS( SELECT pts.DAY_KEY, pts.TRX_NBR, pts.CARD_NBR FROM BIA_RTL.DWB_X_RTL_TRX_POINTS pts WHERE pts.DAY_KEY BETWEEN '20180226' AND '20180304' AND pts.TRX_NBR IN (SELECT TRX_NBR FROM voids) GROUP BY pts.DAY_KEY, pts.TRX_NBR, pts.CARD_NBR ), tendr AS( SELECT tl.DAY_KEY, tl.TRX_NBR, MIN(CASE WHEN tl.TNDR_TYP_CD = '17' THEN tl.CAT_CUST_ACCT_CARD_NBR END) AS SD_CARD, -- staff disc MIN(CASE WHEN tl.TNDR_TYP_CD = '16' THEN tl.CAT_CUST_ACCT_CARD_NBR END) AS CARD4, -- card SUM(CASE WHEN tl.TNDR_TYP_CD = '1' AND tl.ACTN_CD IS NULL THEN tl.TNDR_AMT ELSE 0 END) AS CASH_AMT, -- cash SUM(CASE WHEN tl.TNDR_TYP_CD = '16' AND tl.ACTN_CD IS NULL THEN tl.TNDR_AMT ELSE 0 END) AS CARD_AMT, -- card SUM(CASE WHEN tl.TNDR_TYP_CD NOT IN ('1', '16') AND tl.ACTN_CD IS NULL THEN tl.TNDR_AMT ELSE 0 END) AS OTHERS_AMT, -- other SUM(tl.TNDR_AMT) AS TRX_AMT FROM BIA_ RTL.DWB_RTL_TNDR_LI tl WHERE tl.DAY_KEY BETWEEN '20180226' AND '20180304' AND tl.ACTN_CD IS NULL AND tl.TRX_NBR IN (SELECT TRX_NBR FROM voids) GROUP BY tl.DAY_KEY, tl.TRX_NBR ORDER BY 1 ) SELECT substr(voids.DAY_KEY, 1, 4) || '-' || substr(voids.DAY_KEY, 5, 2)||'-'|| substr(voids.DAY_KEY, 7, 2) as "DATE", voids.STORE_NBR, voids.POS, voids.OPERATOR_NBR, voids.SKU_ITEM_KEY, voids.TRX_NBR, voids.QTY, voids.VOID_AMT, pts.CARD_NBR, tendr.SD_CARD, tendr.CARD4, NVL(tendr.CASH_AMT, 0) AS CASH_AMT, NVL(tendr.CARD_AMT, 0) AS CARD_AMT, NVL(tendr.OTHERS_AMT, 0) AS OTHERS_AMT, NVL(tendr.TRX_AMT, 0) AS TRX_AMT FROM voids LEFT JOIN pts ON (voids.DAY_KEY = pts.DAY_KEY AND voids.TRX_NBR = pts.TRX_NBR) LEFT JOIN tendr ON (voids.DAY_KEY = tendr.DAY_KEY AND voids.TRX_NBR = tendr.TRX_NBR)

Interconnect Ping Latency Stats

  • Ping latency of the roundtrip of a message from this instance to
  • target instances.
  • The target instance is identified by an instance number.
  • Average and standard deviation of ping latency is given in miliseconds
  • for message sizes of 500 bytes and 8K.
  • Note that latency of a message from the instance to itself is used as
  • control, since message latency can include wait for CPU
